Third-party themes vendored into src/presets/
=============================================

Everything under `src/presets/` is GENERATED by `scripts/vendor-themes.mjs` from
the sources below. Do not edit those files by hand — re-run the script.

Eight themes are taken from Visual Studio Code's bundled theme extensions:

    dark-modern, light-modern, monokai, solarized-dark, solarized-light,
    abyss, high-contrast-dark, tomorrow-night-blue

  Source:  https://github.com/microsoft/vscode  (extensions/theme-*)
  Licence: MIT

One theme is taken from the `@shikijs/themes` package, which redistributes it
from the One Dark Pro VS Code extension:

    one-dark-pro

  Source:  https://github.com/shikijs/shiki  (packages/themes)
  Licence: MIT

